message.body: Hey, are you riding lucky today?
If u want, I can, it your day though so I wasn't planning to take him away from you! :)
Either way! Dollar and possibly Louie are up too so I definitely don't feel deprived :) just let me know?
Well, since I don't have help tonight I really only have time for 1 and would like to ride Bach if its all the same to you :) thanks!! has lucky been behaving? :)
Sounds good! He's been super all weekend :)
